data.description: Step into the warmth and comfort of this inviting 2 bedroom, 2-bathroom, with an amazing bonus room 1 story home in the heart of Tyler, TX. With 1,574 sq ft of thoughtfully designed living space, this residence welcomes you with open arms. The bonus room could easily be a 3rd bedroom!  The living area provides a snug retreat, ideal for gatherings or tranquil evenings by the fireplace. Abundant natural light bathes the space through large windows, cultivating an airy and inviting ambiance. The kitchen is thoughtfully designed with ample counter space and includes a built-in microwave for added convenience.  Discover two tranquil bedrooms, each offering a retreat for rest and relaxation. The master suite is a private oasis with an attached bathroom for ultimate convenience. One additional bedroom and a bonus room provide flexibility for guests, a home office, or whatever suits your lifestyle.  Two bathrooms ensure convenience and privacy, enhancing the functionality of this charming home. The neutral color palette throughout creates a versatile canvas for you to infuse your personal style and make it truly yours.  Step outside to a generous backyard, a perfect space for entertaining, gardening, or lazy Sunday afternoons. The outdoor area is a blank canvas, ready for your creativity to bring it to life. Already equipped with RV parking, a carport and 30 amp service.   This residence is conveniently located in the heart of Tyler and near schools, parks, and all the amenities Tyler has to offer. The welcoming community atmosphere makes this home more than just a residence – it's a place to call home.  Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, a growing family, or someone looking to downsize, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Come and experience the warmth and charm of this lovely property – where every detail has been thoughtfully crafted to create a home that you'll love coming home to.
